metadata.name: The Original Emodoge
metadata.description:
Emodoge in emo cave
Dark is always here to stay
Too damn bored to misbehave
Rocket take the pain away

This first piece of seven in our limited series marks the beginning of Emodoge and the birth of a movement.

Emodoge is here to help each of us understand our feelings, be aware of our daily emotions, and know that we are never alone. Join us in our journey to support mental health awareness. Your mental health matters.

A percentage of the primary sale from this piece goes towards mental health charity. 

Number: 1 of 1
Creator: Morningstar
Dimensions: 4267x4267
